headline: Is Costco a Buy, Sell, or Hold in 2025?
summary: Costco (NASDAQ: COST) has delivered fantastic growth in recent years thanks to its ability to offer customers bargain prices on everything from food to gas.  The tariffs are a particular worry for retailers like Costco that import certain products -- which soon may be more expensive -- and at the same time promise customers low prices.  Considering these positive and negative points, is Costco a buy, sell, or hold in 2025?
